Puppet module: rsnapshot

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages rsnapshot software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include rsnapshot              # Install and run rsnapshot with standard configurations.
include rsnapshot::disable     # Disable rsnapshot service.
include rsnapshot::disableboot # Disable rsnapshot service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include rsnapshot::absent      # Remove rsnapshot package.

DEPENDENCIES:
